{"tid":2326510,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北京增一宗香港輸入確診個案　患者結束隔離後發病","createTime":"2020-12-15T11:09:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T12:09:06.000Z","uid":241764,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bcc38963cdafb898b946466e4ebcee3b63a856a2","tid":2326510,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T11:09:24.000Z","msg":"北京昨日新增一宗由香港輸入的新型肺炎確診個案，該名27歲吉林男患者上月28日乘搭香港航空HX336航班抵達北京時，以及在酒店隔離期間，病毒檢測結果呈陰性，上星期六隔離結束，入住另一間酒店後，翌日發病。<br />\n<br />\n當局表示，累計已核實177名密切接觸者，已落實管控措施，目前無異常情況，已經消毒他居住的酒店及就診場所等，並收集有關酒店30個環境樣本，包括電梯、走廊等，當中有4個對病毒呈陽性反應，另外111個涉及公共場所的環境樣本，則對病毒呈陰性反應。<br />\n<br />\n全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565438-20201215.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565438-20201215.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGPFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=371e1f0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565438-20201215.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=908fb9fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565438-20201215.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"88466d2c67ad3e0abc7340d152b486a968597776","tid":2326510,"uid":54930,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T11:10:24.000Z","msg":"狡猾得你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d9a43ddf3e284a6ce720a550f1ff3556a52dc1","tid":2326510,"uid":147376,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T11:10:41.000Z","msg":"光復中国 武肺革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daf529de84fa532a247039bdbd6717cacf446ea9","tid":2326510,"uid":81345,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T11:11:23.000Z","msg":"香港係咪有單類似咁<br />\n但計本地<img src=